question: Are there any castles in the United States?
sparql: PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> ask where {?uri dct:subject dbc:Castles_in_the_United_States}

question: Can you find frescoes in Crete?
sparql: PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> ask where { ?uri dct:subject dbc:Minoan_frescos . ?uri dbp:museum ?museum . ?museum dbo:location dbr:Crete . }

question: Do Urdu and Persian have a common root?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> ask where { dbr:Urdu dbo:languageFamily ?uri . dbr:Persian_language dbo:languageFamily ?uri . }

question: Does the Ford Motor Company have a manufacturing plant in Malaysia?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> ask where { ?uri dbo:assembly dbr:Malaysia . ?uri dbo:manufacturer dbr:Ford_Motor_Company . }

question: How many years was the Ford Model T manufactured?
sparql: PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT (year(xsd:date(?end))-year(xsd:date(?start)) AS ?years) WHERE { res:Ford_Model_T dbo:productionEndYear ?end. res:Ford_Model_T dbo:productionStartYear ?start. }

question: Give me all American presidents in the last 20 years.
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Person . ?uri dct:subject dbc:Presidents_of_the_United_States . ?uri dbp:termEnd ?termEnd . FILTER(year(NOW()) - year(?termEnd) <= 20) }

question: Give me all gangsters from the prohibition era.
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri dbo:occupation dbr:Gangster . ?uri dct:subject dbc:Prohibition-era_gangsters . }

question: Give me all Seven Wonders of the Ancient World.
sparql: PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> select ?uri where { ?uri dct:subject dbc:Seven_Wonders_of_the_Ancient_World }

question: Give me all chemical elements.
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri rdf:type owl:Thing . ?uri dct:subject dbc:Chemical_elements . }

question: How many rivers and lakes are in South Carolina?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> select (COUNT(distinct ?uri) as ?count) where { { ?uri dbo:location dbr:South_Carolina . ?uri rdf:type dbo:Lake . } UNION { ?uri dct:subject dbc:Rivers_and_streams_of_South_Carolina . } }

question: How many states are in Mexico?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> select (count(?uri) as ?count) where { ?uri dbo:type dbr:States_of_Mexico }

question: How many theories did Albert Einstein come up with?
sparql: PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select (count(?uri) as ?count) where { dbr:Albert_Einstein dbo:knownFor ?uri}

question: Is horse racing a sport?
sparql: PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> ask where { dbr:Horse_racing a dbo:Sport }

question: Is Pluto really a planet?
sparql: PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> ask where { dbr:Pluto a dbo:Planet }

question: Was Sigmund Freud married?
sparql: PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> ask where { dbr:Sigmund_Freud dbo:spouse ?uri }

question: What form of government is found in South Africa?
sparql: PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select ?uri where { dbr:South_Africa dbo:governmentType ?uri }

question: What is the largest state in the United States?
sparql: PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select ?uri where { ?uri dct:subject dbc:States_of_the_United_States. ?uri rdf:type dbo:AdministrativeRegion. ?uri dbo:areaTotal ?area } ORDER BY DESC(?area) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

question: What is the longest river in the world?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select ?uri where { ?uri rdf:type dbo:BodyOfWater . ?uri dbo:length ?length } ORDER BY DESC(?length) LIMIT 1

question: Which building after the Burj Khalifa has the most floors?
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Burj_Khalifa dbo:floorCount ?burj . ?uri rdf:type dbo:Building . ?uri dbo:floorCount ?proj . FILTER(?proj < ?burj) } ORDER BY DESC(?proj) LIMIT 1

question: What is the wavelength of indigo?
sparql: PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select ?n where { dbr:Indigo dbo:wavelength ?n }

question: What was the name of the famous battle in 1836 in San Antonio?
sparql: PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> select ?uri where { ?uri rdf:type dbo:MilitaryConflict. ?uri dbo:place dbr:San_Antonio. ?uri dbo:date ?date. FILTER ( ?date > '1835-12-31T00:00:00Z'^^xsd:dateTime). FILTER ( ?date <= '1836-12-31T00:00:00Z'^^xsd:dateTime) }

question: What were the names of the three ships used by Columbus?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> select ?uri where { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Ship. ?uri dct:subject dbc:Christopher_Columbus. ?uri dct:subject dbc:Exploration_ships. }

question: What were the original 13 British colonies?
sparql: PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri dct:subject dbc:Former_British_colonies. ?uri dct:subject dbc:Thirteen_Colonies. }

question: When did Muhammad die?
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct ?date where { res:Muhammad dbo:deathDate ?date. }

question: When was the De Beers company founded?
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct ?date where { res:De_Beers dbo:foundingYear ?date. }

question: When was John Adams born?
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct ?date where { res:John_Adams dbo:birthDate ?date. }

question: Which American presidents were in office during the Vietnam War?
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> select distinct ?uri where { res:Vietnam_War dbo:commander ?uri . ?uri dct:subject dbc:Presidents_of_the_United_States . }

question: Which city has the oldest running metro?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> select ?loc where { ?uri dbo:type dbr:Rapid_transit . ?uri dbo:openingYear ?date . ?uri dbo:location ?loc . ?loc rdf:type dbo:City . } ORDER BY ASC(?date) LIMIT 1

question: Which holidays are celebrated around the world?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Holiday. }

question: Who assassinated President McKinley?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>  PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Person . ?uri dct:subject dbc:American_assassins . ?uri dct:subject dbc:Assassination_of_William_McKinley . }

question: Who discovered Pluto?
sparql: PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select ?uri where { dbr:Pluto dbo:discoverer ?uri }

question: Who killed Caesar?
sparql: PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri dct:subject dbc:Assassins_of_Julius_Caesar. }

question: Who was buried in the Great Pyramid of Giza?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> select ?uri where { ?uri dbo:restingPlace dbr:Great_Pyramid_of_Giza . }

question: Who was the first King of England?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Royalty. ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatEnglishMonarchs . ?uri dbo:activeYearsStartYear ?date . } ORDER BY ASC(?date) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

question: What was the final result of the War of the Roses?
sparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> select distinct ?result where { ?uri dbo:isPartOfMilitaryConflict dbr:Wars_of_the_Roses. ?uri dbo:result ?result . ?uri dbo:date ?date } ORDER BY DESC(?date) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

question: Who writes the Farmers' Almanac?
sparql: PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> select ?uri where { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Farmers'_Almanac> dbp:editor ?uri. }

question: How big is the earth's diameter?
sparql: PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct (xsd:double(?radius)*2 AS ?diameter) where { res:Earth dbo:meanRadius ?radius . }

question: When did Paraguay proclaim its independence?
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> select distinct ?date where { res:Paraguay dbp:establishedDate ?date . }

question: How many people live in Eurasia?
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct ?population where { res:Eurasia dbo:populationTotal ?population . }

question: Give me the runtime of Toy Story.
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct ?runtime where { res:Toy_Story dbo:runtime ?runtime . }

question: What was the first name of the band Queens of the Stone Age?
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct ?name where { res:Queens_of_the_Stone_Age dbo:alias ?name . }

question: Give me the birth place of Frank Sinatra.
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct ?place where { res:Frank_Sinatra dbo:birthPlace ?place . }

question: Which university did Angela Merkel attend?
sparql: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct ?university where { res:Angela_Merkel dbo:almaMater ?university . }
